  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras/f746379da287392197db122a5a4aa45d.avif?t=1751521277\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras_big/f746379da287392197db122a5a4aa45d.avif?t=1751521277 width=800 height=212 /></span>Interact with bizarre mechanisms, think out of the box to gain your freedom, and discover historical mysteries</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras/5eb164584996008508a2c86445f94f0f.avif?t=1751521277\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras_big/5eb164584996008508a2c86445f94f0f.avif?t=1751521277 width=800 height=212 /></span>You will experience a real-life adventure while playing this puzzle game! Lots of intriguing puzzles are waiting for you, ensuring an immersive experience that will keep you engaged for hours</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras/619fc10b3fc4e4d41b03da55fb9936cb.avif?t=1751521277\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras_big/619fc10b3fc4e4d41b03da55fb9936cb.avif?t=1751521277 width=800 height=212 /></span>Examine several mechanisms to unlock each box and gain your freedom </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras/d0fbf300b73b21080cb5254306264441.avif?t=1751521277\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras_big/d0fbf300b73b21080cb5254306264441.avif?t=1751521277 width=800 height=212 /></span>For an unforgettable experience, immerse yourself in the adventure by playing the game with your headphones on!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras/cb9edc271760aa613cfb904c63cf134d.avif?t=1751521277\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras_big/cb9edc271760aa613cfb904c63cf134d.avif?t=1751521277 width=800 height=212 /></span>Get hints that will help you through the game. If you really can't make it, you may still get in touch with the developer, who will be happy to help ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras/6b8d6a6879d67c9743ccf91106271b63.avif?t=1751521277\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras_big/6b8d6a6879d67c9743ccf91106271b63.avif?t=1751521277 width=800 height=212 /></span>This is an extra challenge that will keep your brain busy for days. Open the letter inside the Enigmas Box and crack a new riddle every day. How far can you go? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras/a1ef435bf16d1f717e765ef3b9afb87e.poster.avif?t=1751521277\" width=614 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras/a1ef435bf16d1f717e765ef3b9afb87e.webm?t=1751521277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras/a1ef435bf16d1f717e765ef3b9afb87e.mp4?t=1751521277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras/90431feed7988ed8fd215ff997ec39e9.avif?t=1751521277\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras_big/90431feed7988ed8fd215ff997ec39e9.avif?t=1751521277 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Available in English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Russian, and Japanese.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The game language will change automatically based on the language settings of your device</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1751521277\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras_big/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1751521277 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong>'s here, I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of  <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing all by myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i>If you like my works, consider leaving a review here on Steam, your support will be greatly appreciated!</i></strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras/f746379da287392197db122a5a4aa45d.avif?t=1751521277\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras_big/f746379da287392197db122a5a4aa45d.avif?t=1751521277 width=800 height=212 /></span>Interact with bizarre mechanisms, think out of the box to gain your freedom, and discover historical mysteries</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras/5eb164584996008508a2c86445f94f0f.avif?t=1751521277\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras_big/5eb164584996008508a2c86445f94f0f.avif?t=1751521277 width=800 height=212 /></span>You will experience a real-life adventure while playing this puzzle game! Lots of intriguing puzzles are waiting for you, ensuring an immersive experience that will keep you engaged for hours</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras/619fc10b3fc4e4d41b03da55fb9936cb.avif?t=1751521277\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras_big/619fc10b3fc4e4d41b03da55fb9936cb.avif?t=1751521277 width=800 height=212 /></span>Examine several mechanisms to unlock each box and gain your freedom </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras/d0fbf300b73b21080cb5254306264441.avif?t=1751521277\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700460/extras_big/d0fbf300b73b21080cb52543062